/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_PV_GetUnitFromGiftwrapPIF                      
** Short Desc: A data extract from GiftWrap, which gives total units for selected PIF accounts 
**                      
** Full Description: A data extract from GiftWrap, which gives total units for selected PIF accounts 
**      
**                              
** Input Arguments:   		@XMLCustomerAccountNumber XML
**	,@ValuationDate DATETIME           
** Sample Call     
       
 EXEC dbo.USP_PV_GetUnitFromGiftwrapPIF  @XMLCustomerAccountNumber = '<CustomerAccountCollection>    
      <InsertList>    
      <CustomerAccount CustomerAccountNumber="WMPIF3" />    
      </InsertList>    
      </CustomerAccountCollection>',    
  @ValuationDate = '12/31/2013'    
